{"thag6.11:0.1":"Theragatha 6.11 ","thag6.11:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.11:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.11:0.4":"Nhatakamunittheragatha ","thag6.11:1.1":"“Vatarogabhinito tvam, ","thag6.11:1.2":"viharam kanane vane; ","thag6.11:1.3":"Paviddhagocare lukhe, ","thag6.11:1.4":"katham bhikkhu karissasi”. ","thag6.11:2.1":"“Pitisukhena vipulena, ","thag6.11:2.2":"pharitvana samussayam; ","thag6.11:2.3":"Lukhampi abhisambhonto, ","thag6.11:2.4":"viharissami kanane. ","thag6.11:3.1":"Bhavento satta bojjhange, ","thag6.11:3.2":"indriyani balani ca; ","thag6.11:3.3":"Jhanasokhummasampanno, ","thag6.11:3.4":"viharissam anasavo. ","thag6.11:4.1":"Vippamuttam kilesehi, ","thag6.11:4.2":"suddhacittam anavilam; ","thag6.11:4.3":"Abhinham paccavekkhanto, ","thag6.11:4.4":"viharissam anasavo. ","thag6.11:5.1":"Ajjhattanca bahiddha ca, ","thag6.11:5.2":"ye me vijjimsu asava; ","thag6.11:5.3":"Sabbe asesa ucchinna, ","thag6.11:5.4":"na ca uppajjare puna. ","thag6.11:6.1":"Pancakkhandha parinnata, ","thag6.11:6.2":"titthanti chinnamulaka; ","thag6.11:6.3":"Dukkhakkhayo anuppatto, ","thag6.11:6.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo”ti. ","thag6.11:6.5":"… Nhatakamunitthero …. "}